Compile a CPP file to generate executable target file:

    g++ hello.cpp
    Creates ./a.exe

Compile the file_name and not assembling or linking

    g++ -S file_name
    Creates file_name.s assembly file

Compile and assemble the file_name and not link the object code to produce executable file

    g++ -c file_name.cpp
    Creates file_name.o object code

Compiles and links file_name

    g++ -o main.exe file_name.cpp
    Creates main.exe executable
